text: István Séllyei (8 June 1950 - 19 July 2020) was a Hungarian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman 90 kg at the 1976 Summer Olympics. He was born in Eger, Hungary. Séllyei died in Budapest on 19 July 2020, aged 70. ==References== ==Other websites== * * * Category:1950 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Olympians for Hungary Category:Hungarian wrestlers
